data.title: West Virginia Former Attorneys General
data.meta_description: Find individuals who have previously served as attorney general of West Virginia. This list may not be all inclusive of former attorneys general.
data.text:
A chronological list of past West Virginia attorneys general is below.

Return to full list of past attorneys general or learn more about the current West Virginia Attorney General.

Darrell V. McGraw, Jr. 1993 – 2013 Mario J. Palumbo 1991 – 1993 Roger Tompkins 1989 – 1991 Charles G. Brown 1985 – 1989 Chauncey H. Browning 1969 – 1985 John G. Fox 1952 – 1957 William C. Marland 1949 – 1952 Ira J. Partlow 1945 – 1949 Ira J. Partlow (Acting) 1943 – 1945 James Kay Thomas 1943 – 1945 William S. Wysong 1942 – 1943 Ira J. Partlow (Acting) 1942 Clarence W. Meadows 1937 – 1942 Homer A. Holt 1933 – 1937 Howard B. Lee 1925 – 1933 E. T. England 1917 – 1925 A. A. Lilly 1913 – 1917 William G. Conley 1908 – 1913 Clarke W. May 1905 – 1908
